1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 49-02 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to public service commission requirements for open meetings.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 49-02 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Public service commission open meetings.
7 Except as otherwise provided by law, a meeting of the public service commission is subject
8 to the requirements of chapter 44 - 04. A meeting of the public service commission does no t
9 include a quorum of members attending a standing legislative committee. The public service
10 commission is exempt from posting notice at the location of a meeting, as required under
11 section 44 - 04 - 20, if the meeting was not scheduled or organized by the public service
12 commission.
